{"tid":608733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人廿幾歲都仲係要父母照顧，自己唔識得關心佢地？","createTime":"2018-03-28T11:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T13:09:17.000Z","uid":18971,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62a50346f538661cb8c2c533ea3749ba91c1b82d","tid":608733,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"成二十幾歲人都仲係要父母照顧，唔識得主動關心佢地。唔識煮野食，老母日日放工都要買菜煮飯，有時又好懶自己唔肯幫手做家務，老母返工煮飯洗碗做家務一腳踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n畢左業做左一年野之後依家仲要失埋業，日日係屋企過左3個月。老母時不時叫我搵工但都仲未搵到。永遠都係老豆老母打電話比自己，講2句就急著收佢地線，自己就唔識得主動打比佢地關心佢地，之前老豆出國公幹左2個星期都無打過一次電話比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯一叫做孝順佢地既就係返工個一年每個月都比一半糧做家用。<br />\n<br />\n點解成20幾歲人都仲咁廢嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9e0359e8ba5ae97d24ca763f39899bf7090db7","tid":608733,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"第日到佢地病重既時候就會後悔點解以前冇好好分擔父母既工作量"},{"pid":"91f954f4b04741048ebeb97135c62d7cf7519caa","tid":608733,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9e0359e8ba5ae97d24ca763f39899bf7090db7","tid":608733,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"第日到佢地病重既時候就會後悔點解以前冇好好分擔父母既工作量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529ac0b55e9cd7abac56d81bd22a7980d849a0c1","tid":608733,"uid":162959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"你唔講仲以為係我開post tim 我好過你少少 就係識煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7797bc0e7273e39ce37a0ab86589735d9d1da45","tid":608733,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"529ac0b55e9cd7abac56d81bd22a7980d849a0c1","tid":608733,"uid":162959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"你唔講仲以為係我開post tim 我好過你少少 就係識煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8006bbab62adbdcca07ddf1cc23104c7ecbb6815","tid":608733,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"個個都咁孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"80c8a4000819a4bded043e0f4d52305a4ea3aff3","tid":608733,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"知道自己有問題仲唔去改咁你就真係有問題"},{"pid":"646bff5ac0e26c210f9b419278bbe9fba2fe662b","tid":608733,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:10:44.000Z","msg":"煮嘢食做家務有幾難"},{"pid":"5764201c4e2450f1aada0742fb50d8d0bf0078d6","tid":608733,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553a19cf900965405df03937c5cdb55070b7c829","tid":608733,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"step 1 搵份hea工做住先<br />\n<br />\nstep 2 自動做家務<br />\n<br />\nstep 3 開始煎下蛋 炒下菜"},{"pid":"93a35a4500d1e8a895f3d5ec4cce6f81be12900e","tid":608733,"uid":18971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"553a19cf900965405df03937c5cdb55070b7c829","tid":608733,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"step 1 搵份hea工做住先<br />\n<br />\nstep 2 自動做家務<br />\n<br